## Rule Template

Create new rules using this structure:

**With description (contextual application)**
```markdown
---
description: Brief description of what this rule addresses and why it's important
alwaysApply: false
---
# [Rule Name]
```

**With file globs (deterministic application)**
```markdown
---
globs: *.tsx, src/config/**/*.json, *Test.cpp
alwaysApply: false
---
# [Rule Name]
```

